Title: An Act Changing the Name of the San Jose City National High School in the Province of Nueva Ecija to Constancio Padilla National High School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 650
An Act Changing the Name of the San Jose City National High School in the Province of Nueva Ecija to Constancio Padilla National High School
Section 1. The name of the San Jose City National High School in the Province of Nueva Ecija is changed to Constancio Padilla National High School.1avvphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 7, 1984
